    },
    {
      "name": "Lime Juice",
      "amount": "2 tbsp",
      "notes": "freshly squeezed"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "1. In a large bowl, combine the crispy corn, sweet red onion, and Thai red chili flakes.",
    "2. In a small bowl, whisk together the French corn salad dressing, lime juice, salt, and sugar.",
    "3. Pour the dressing over the corn mixture and toss to coat.",
    "4. Stir in chopped fresh cilantro.",
    "5. Taste and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "6. Cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "7. Just before serving, give the salad a good stir and adjust the seasoning if needed.",
    "8. Serve chilled or at room temperature."
